subject: Wrestling
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Iowa State advanced 9 of its 10 qualifiers to take the lead after the first round of the N.C.A.A. championships with 25 points. Iowa, the favorite to repeat as champion, was second with 22 points and eight wrestlers in the championship bracket. ncaa.
